detail_desc: Fitted jersey dress with long, straight sleeves. Unlined.
Cardigan in a fine-knit cotton blend containing some wool. Ribbed collar, buttons down the front and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Trousers in soft organic cotton jersey with an elasticated waist, pleats at the front and fake front pockets.
Sleeveless, calf-length dress in soft jersey made from a cotton blend. Low-cut neckline and slits in the sides.
Trousers in soft sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and ribbed hems. Soft brushed inside.
Shorts in patterned cotton twill with a zip fly and button, coin pocket, side pockets and welt back pockets.
Imitation suede boots with a fold-down shaft and an opening at the back with a hook and loop fastening. Faux fur linings and insoles and fluted soles.

Single-breasted jacket in linen and cotton chambray with narrow notch lapels, a chest pocket, flap welt front pockets and two inner pockets. Two buttons at the front, a button at the cuffs and a single back vent. Lined. Skinny Fit – a slightly shorter style that shapes in at the chest and tapers sharply at the waist. This combined with narrow shoulders and sleeves creates a completely fitted silhouette.
Short-sleeved polo shirt in cotton piqué with a ribbed collar, zip at the top and slits in the sides.
5-pocket low-rise shorts in twill with hard-worn details, a button fly and skinny legs with seams across the front.

Single-breasted jacket in a slightly stretchy weave. Notch lapels with a decorative buttonhole, a chest pocket, patch front pockets and one inner pocket. Two buttons at the front, decorative buttons at the cuffs and a double back vent. Lined. Slim Fit – a fit that shapes in at the chest and tapers at the waist. This, combined with slightly narrower sleeves, creates a fitted silhouette.
Padded jacket with a detachable, padded, lined hood, high collar, zip down the front and side pockets . Lined.

Bra with self-adhesive cups and no shoulder straps or back making it perfect for wearing under strapless or backless garments. Front fastening. Moulded, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Can be washed and reused.
Pile jacket with a hood, zip down the front with a chin guard and kangaroo pockets. Ribbed trims around the pockets and cuffs.

Suit trousers in a stretch weave with a concealed hook-and-eye fastener and zip fly. Diagonal side pockets, jetted back pockets with a button, and legs with creases. Super skinny fit – a fit with slightly shorter legs that is close-fitting at the thighs, knees and ankles to create a completely fitted silhouette.
Calf-length, pleated skirt in airy crêpe with a high waist, side fastening and wrapover front. Unlined.
Imitation leather mules with pointed toes, open sides and round, leopard-print heels. Satin linings, imitation leather insoles and rubber soles. Heel 4 cm.
5-pocket slim-fit jeans in supersoft, stretch denim with an adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and legs with seams and narrow hems.
Long-sleeved top in sweatshirt fabric with a print motif and ribbing around the neckline and cuffs. An extended, rounded hem in woven fabric with decorative buttons.
Short dress in a lightly crêped weave with a collar, buttons down the front and a yoke with a pleat at the back. Short sleeves, a flap chest pocket and a narrow tie belt at the waist. Unlined.
Brazilian briefs in lace with a low waist, lined gusset, wide sides and half-string back.
Short shorts in sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated, drawstring jersey waistband, side pockets and rounded hems.
5-pocket ankle-length jeans in washed stretch denim with hard-worn details in a slightly looser fit with a regular waist, zip fly and button and tapered legs with raw-edge hems.
Pyjamas with a shirt and bottoms in soft satin. Short-sleeved shirt with notch lapels and buttons down the front. Wide, ankle-length bottoms with an elasticated waist.
KAROLINA KIJAK x H&M. T-shirt in soft slub cotton jersey with a ribbed trim around the neckline and short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups.
Fitted top in soft, rib-knit wool containing some cashmere with a round neck and long sleeves.
5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed cotton denim with an extra-high waist and zip fly and button. Slightly looser fit with straight legs. The cotton content of the jeans is partly recycled.
Long-sleeved blouse in a softly draping weave with a collar, concealed buttons down the front and a yoke with a pleat at the back. Slightly wider sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem.

Long-sleeved shirt in soft cotton twill with a collar, buttons down the front and small embroidered detail on the chest. Contrasting colour on the inside of the collar stand and cuffs, and a rounded hem.
Wide jumper in a soft, rib-knit cotton blend with a V-neck, gently dropped shoulders, long sleeves and slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.

Long-sleeved dress in airy, patterned chiffon with a small, gathered stand-up collar and buttons at the front. Long raglan sleeves with covered elastication at the cuffs and a gathered seam at the waist. Sleeveless underdress in jersey.
Sleeveless dress in soft, patterned cotton jersey. Narrow cut at the top with short shoulder straps, a seam at the waist and a gently flared skirt.
Sandals with wide, crossover straps, square toes and low heels. Satin linings, imitation leather insoles and rubber soles. Heel 1.5 cm.
Long-sleeved top in soft, airy jersey.
Cropped hooded top in sweatshirt fabric with dropped shoulders and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Round-necked T-shirt in organic cotton jersey.
Swim shorts in woven fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and a welt back pocket with a hook and loop fastener. Soft mesh inner shorts.
T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a round neckline and a print motif.

Padded parka with a pile-lined hood with a tab and press-stud at the top. Zip and wind flap with press-studs down the front, handwarmer pockets and flap patch pockets with a concealed press-stud. Elasticated, partially concealed drawstring at the hem. Lined.
Cotton jersey briefs.
A-line dress in patterned lightweight sweatshirt fabric with long sleeves and a detachable braided imitation suede belt.
Oversized top in sweatshirt fabric with a lined hood with a wrapover front. Kangaroo pocket, dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
5-pocket jeans in washed denim with a regular waist, button fly and tapered legs.
Fitted jacket in a sturdy, textured-weave wool blend with frayed edges. Notch lapels, welt front pockets and decorative buttons at the front and cuffs. No fasteners. Lined.
Blouse in an airy cotton weave with a small, gathered stand-up collar, buttons down the front, long balloon sleeves with narrow elastication at the cuffs, and a rounded hem.
Long-sleeved, off-the-shoulder top in sweatshirt fabric with ribbing around the top, cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside
Cap in cotton twill with embroidered text on the front and an adjustable tab and fastener at the back.
Loafers with cut-out sections at the sides, satin linings, imitation leather insoles and rubber soles. Heel 3 cm.

Shopper in a sturdy cotton weave with tassels at the sides, a patterned front and two handles at the top that continue down the sides. Magnetic fastener at the top and one zipped inner compartment. Lined. Depth 10 cm. Height 32.5 cm. Width 48 cm.

Dress in a patterned viscose weave with a V-neck and sewn-in wrapover with a concealed press-stud at the front. 3/4-length sleeves with slits at the cuffs, and an elasticated seam at the waist. Unlined.

Balconette bra in microfibre and lace with underwired, padded cups that lift and shape. Narrow, detachable shoulder straps that can be fastened in several different ways and a fastening at the back with three pairs of hooks and eyes.
Loafers with tassels and a moccasin seam at the front. Leather linings and insoles and thermoplastic rubber (TPR) soles. Heel approx. 3 cm.
Fitted T-shirt in ribbed jersey made from a silk and viscose blend with a round neck and short sleeves.
Long-sleeved top in a linen weave with a V-neck. Slightly longer at the back.
Soft, non-wired bras in lace with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps, removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support, and a lace trim at the hem. No fasteners.
Sports jacket in fast-drying functional fabric with a mesh-lined hood and zip down the front with a chin guard. Front pockets and long raglan sleeves. Soft brushed inside.
Smartphone case in faux fur with an imitation leather lining, three card compartments and a larger note compartment. Press-stud fastening.

Sleeveless dress in glittery tulle strewn with fabric flower appliqués. Opening with a pearly button at the back of the neck, and a gathered seam with tiers at the waist and hem to create width in the skirt. Lined.
Blouse in an airy, patterned crêpe weave with a small, frilled collar, opening with a concealed button at the back of the neck, short puff sleeves and a straight-cut hem.
Thin tights with an elasticated waist.
Fitted jumper in a soft rib knit with a V-neck, buttons at the top and long sleeves.

EMMA JAYNE x H&M. Set with a vest top and pair of shorts in soft, patterned cotton jersey. Vest top with a text print on the front and ribbed trim around the neckline and armholes. Shorts with an elasticated, drawstring waist.
Pleated, calf-length skirt in woven fabric with covered elastication at the waist. Lined.

5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed, stretch denim with worn details. High waist, zip fly and button and skinny legs. Embrace – denim with a smart stretch function that moulds to the body for a comfortable, flattering silhouette.
Joggers in cotton sweatshirt fabric with a washed look. Elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and tapered legs with ribbed hems.
Short, A-line, jersey dress made from a modal and cotton blend.
Jumper in soft, fine-knit cotton with buttons at the back of the neck and a rounded collar in woven fabric. Longer layer in woven fabric at the hem.
Oversized cardigan in a soft, chunky knit with a deep V-neck, buttons down the front and ribbing around the opening. Low dropped shoulders and wide sleeves with ribbed cuffs.
Jacquard-knit socks in a soft cotton blend with elasticated tops.
Sandals with covered heels and an adjustable ankle strap with a hook and loop fastening. Imitation leather insoles and fluted soles.
Thin metal chain necklaces with a rod-shaped pendant. Adjustable length 51-58 cm and 77-84 cm. Length of pendants 4.5 cm and 5.5 cm.
5-pocket trousers in stretch twill with a regular waist and slim legs.
Leggings in soft cotton jersey with an elasticated waist.
A pair of oval earrings made from recycled zinc.

Knitted all-in-one suit with a stand-up collar, zip down the front with a chin guard, long raglan sleeves and narrow elastication at the cuffs and hems. Soft, thermal fleece inside. The polyester content of the suit is partly recycled.
Top in sweatshirt fabric with a print motif on the front, a lined hood, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.

Car coat in woven fabric with a slight sheen. Collar, concealed buttons down the front and long, lined sleeves with an adjustable tab at the cuffs. Welt side pockets, one inner pocket and a single back vent.
Short, 5-pocket shorts in washed denim with hard-worn details in a slightly looser fit with a regular waist, zip fly with a button and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Trousers in washed stretch cotton twill with a zip fly and button and front and back pockets. Slim fit with narrow hems.
V-neck blouse in a crêpe weave with short, lace-trimmed sleeves. Lined.
